=====Usage notes=====
* In Cantonese, {{l|yue|食|tr=sik<sup>6</sup>}} is the most common term for "eating" and {{l-self|zh|吔|tr=jaak<sup>3</sup>}} is considered less polite than the former.
* When playing mahjong, a player may say this word as a call when forming a chow on another player's discard.

